                    </imageobject>
                </inlinemediaobject> button <emphasis>after you have added an accounting
                    line</emphasis>:</para>
            <para role="Normal"/>
            <para role="Normal">
                <screenshot>
                    <mediaobject>
                        <alt>Current Items: Accounting Line. Displaying the Bal Inquiry button</alt>
                        <imageobject>
                            <imagedata
                                fileref="../images/ManagingAndEncumberingFundsNoTitlePagePt2-273.png"
                                width="100%"/>
                        </imageobject>
                    </mediaobject>
                </screenshot>
            </para>
            <para role="Normal">From the <emphasis role="bold">Balance Inquiry Report
                    Menu</emphasis>, select <emphasis role="bold">Available Balances</emphasis>: </para>
            <para role="Normal">
                <inlinemediaobject>
                    <alt>Balance Inquiry Report Menu</alt>
                    <imageobject>
                        <imagedata
                            fileref="../images/ManagingAndEncumberingFundsNoTitlePagePt2-274.png"/>
                    </imageobject>
                </inlinemediaobject></para>
            <para role="Normal">To return to the requisition, click the <inlinemediaobject>
